author: oO Onaeko Oo
text:
So you want to hear a horror story? Well then, but I'm not good remembering things.

It was a quite ago when I met my friends inside the walls, the big and dusty towers that protected the village. We planned on going to the store so we could kill the time before summer holidays.

But suddenly, the clouds started getting darker. Cold drops hit our necks an hour way back home.

Suddenly, lightning bolts started to destroy the village, while the ground moved side to side violently.
A giant monster with her most angry face appeared, opening her mouth to eat everyone...


But instead of that..


She said...


"Nya nYA~"...


We don't talk about that day since then...
